intenance. \n<br />\n<br />Symptoms: \n<br />• Inability to access web, SSH, or FTP on DV. \n<br />• Inability to access email on Grid.</p>      \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 28 Oct 2016 00:59:33 -0700\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/trxmhbc8zjq7\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/trxmhbc8zjq7\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:40:\"\n      \n      \n      \n      \n      \n    \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28:\"Network Hardware Maintenance\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1335:\"\n<p><small>Oct 27, 22:39 PDT</small><br><strong>Completed</strong> - Due to unforeseen issues, this maintenance was rolled back and will be rescheduled.</p><p><small>Oct 27, 21:01 PDT</small><br><strong>In progress</strong> - Scheduled maintenance is currently in progress. We will provide updates as necessary.</p><p><small>Oct 19, 16:44 PDT</small><br><strong>Scheduled</strong> - We will be performing scheduled system maintenance on Thursday, October 27, 2016 to our network infrastructure. Here are the important details:\n<br />\n<br /><b>Who is affected?</b>\n<br />\n<br />This maintenance will affect customers on our DV servers as well as email on our Grid Shared