perational. \n<br />\n<br />Thanks for your patience while we waited out this issue, and let us know if you have any further issues.</p><p><small>Oct 21, 13:45 PDT</small><br><strong>Update</strong> - LiveChat is now available as a support channel.\n<br />\n<br />We thank you for your patience.</p><p><small>Oct 21, 12:44 PDT</small><br><strong>Update</strong> - LiveChat will be offline while we continue to monitor the situation. If you need support, you can call us at the following number:\n<br />310.841.5500</p><p><small>Oct 21, 11:28 PDT</small><br><strong>Monitoring</strong> - The ongoing DDoS is intermittent - services may be coming back online as of now. We\'ll continue to monitor the situation and provide updates as more information is available. \n<br />\n<br />Thanks again for your patience.</p><p><small>Oct 21, 10:16 PDT</small><br><strong>Investigating</strong> - DYN DNS is currently undergoing a DDoS attack. As a result some systems which (mt) Media Temple uses, such as LiveChat, which our agents use to provide chat support to our customers, and our Community pages may be unavailable \n<br />\n<br />We apologize for any inconvenience this issue may be causing, and we appreciate your patience while we wait on a resolution.</p>      \";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 21 Oct 2016 14:25:18 -0700\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/pqyb4z9pz9c0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"http://status.mediatemple.net/incidents/pqyb4z9pz9c0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:10;a:6:{s:4:\"